  "body": "\nNew Loft/Condo for rent<br />\n<br />\nLocation:  240 Bates, Town of Mount Royal / Ville Mont-Royal<br />\n<br />\nSize/Grandeur:  2 Bedrooms, 932 sq feet + Balcony<br />\n<br />\nPrice Includes/ Prix Inclus: 1 indoor heated garage space<br />\n<br />\nPrice/Prix:  1375$ per month.<br />\n<br />\nIncredible location! Situated in the ultra prestigious Town of Mount Royal (TMR), 8 minutes by car or train from Downtown Montreal.  3 min walk from Canora train station. Brand new 2 bedroom Loft/Condo with 12 foot ceilings, great view of TMR, air conditioning, brand new appliances, granite countertops, cacao hardwood floors, open space (Master bedroom does have walls finished up to the ceiling) and very high quality, modern finish. Includes 1 indoor heated garage space plus plenty of free parking nearby. Unit will be available to occupy as of July 1st, 2012. <br />\n<br />\nContact 514-347-9050 for additional information or e-mail at j.nehme @ live.ca<br />\n\n<br /><br />\n\n<!-- START CLTAGS -->\n<br />\n\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG xstreet0=Bates -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG xstreet1= -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG city=Town of Mount Royal -->\n\t\t\t<!-- CLTAG region=QC -->\n\t\t\tBates\n\t\t\t<small>\n\t\t\t\t(<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maps.google.com/?q=loc%3A+Bates+Town+of+Mount+Royal+QC+CA\">google map</a>)\n\t\t\t\t(<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://maps.yahoo.com/maps_result?addr=Bates&amp;csz=Town+of+Mount+Royal+QC&amp;country=CA\">yahoo map</a>)\n\t\t\t</small>\n\t\t<ul class=\"blurbs\">\n<li> <!-- CLTAG GeographicArea=T.M.R. / V.M.R. -->Location: T.M.R. / V.M.R.</li>\n<li>it's NOT ok to contact this poster with services or other commercial interests</li></ul>\n<!-- END CLTAGS -->\n",
